Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.31,0:06:24.28,Sign3,,0,0,0,,{\an2\frz9.5\pos(1125,849)\blur0.65}Kouki
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.61,0:00:10.65,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.65,0:00:12.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you bite your tongue?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.36,0:00:18.53,Default,,0,0,0,,My tooth feels kind of wobbly.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.53,0:00:19.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't touch it! Don't touch it!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.70,0:00:22.00,Default,,0,0,0,,What should I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.00,0:00:26.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm... An adult tooth will be coming in underneath it, so just leave it alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.96,0:00:30.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Would you like me to make porridge from your rice for you?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.59,0:00:33.67,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I'll be fine if I eat it slowly.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.99,0:02:20.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, Daikichi!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.45,0:02:22.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.12,0:02:30.75,Default,,0,0,0,,W-What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.83,0:02:34.63,Default,,0,0,0,,That drawing's mine!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.51,0:02:42.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Your dad is always the one who comes to these things, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.47,0:02:43.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.10,0:02:45.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Although he's not my dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.26,0:02:47.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?! He's not?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.81,0:02:51.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, isn't that great.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.85,0:02:56.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, hey! Rin-chan's the best at drawing in Class B.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.90,0:02:58.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.28,0:03:01.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I bet you could be a mangaka.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.45,0:03:03.24,Default,,0,0,0,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.24,0:03:05.66,Default,,0,0,0,,You could!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.00,0:03:13.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Papa!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.54,0:03:15.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Over here!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.34,0:03:21.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry I'm late.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.84,0:03:25.55,Default,,0,0,0,,This stylish guy is... a father?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.55,0:03:27.01,Default,,0,0,0,,So cool!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.01,0:03:28.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Lucky!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.06,0:03:30.18,Alt,,0,0,0,,He's really tall!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.06,0:03:33.15,Default,,0,0,0,,By the way, Sayaka-chan said her dad is 31, just like you!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.40,0:03:35.36,Default,,0,0,0,,You've got to be kidding me!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.69,0:03:39.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Really? What a pleasant coincidence.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.66,0:03:44.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Papa's a model!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.57,0:03:46.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.62,0:03:48.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Sayaka!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.08,0:03:50.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I've only done a little bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.66,0:03:52.62,Default,,0,0,0,,It was when I was younger...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.96,0:03:59.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I think I might have seen you in our company's catalogue...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.38,0:04:01.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Really?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.26,0:04:03.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Excuse me...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.43,0:04:05.47,Default,,0,0,0,,But if it's not too much trouble, can I ask the name of your company?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.35,0:04:09.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, that's probably me!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.89,0:04:12.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm so grateful!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.52,0:04:13.69,Alt,,0,0,0,,He's cheerful, isn't he?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.31,0:04:13.69,Default,,0,0,0,,This is so embarrassing...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.69,0:04:17.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Nowadays, I'm an office manager, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.15,0:04:18.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.86,0:04:20.65,Default,,0,0,0,,That kind of feels like a waste...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.15,0:04:24.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Modeling's the sort of job where you don't really know where your next paycheck is coming from,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.28,0:04:26.87,Default,,0,0,0,,so when my daughter was born, I decided to call it quits.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.24,0:04:28.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.45,0:04:34.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Back then, I did nothing but drink and complain about work...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.17,0:04:35.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Micchan!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.17,0:04:39.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Nabe-chin! It's been a while!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.46,0:04:42.13,Default,,0,0,0,,We're old classmates.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.13,0:04:43.59,Default,,0,0,0,,We both come from around this area.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.59,0:04:47.22,Default,,0,0,0,,He has a kid, too; a boy in Class A.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.22,0:04:50.26,Default,,0,0,0,,This is Rin-chan's father, Daikichi-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.26,0:04:51.77,Default,,0,0,0,,He's the same age as us.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.06,0:04:53.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Really? Nice to meet you!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.27,0:04:56.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Likewise.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.23,0:05:00.65,Default,,0,0,0,,These two seem like the kind who really look out for their kids.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.65,0:05:01.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Daikichi!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.20,0:05:07.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm a butcher.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.91,0:05:09.49,Default,,0,0,0,,My shop's on the corner of the nearby shopping district.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.49,0:05:12.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, we often buy croquettes there and eat them on the way home.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.20,0:05:14.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Really? Glad to hear it!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.79,0:05:15.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Me, too! Me, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.96,0:05:18.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I know, I know!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.47,0:05:28.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Looks like I've befriended a couple of other fathers.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.04,0:06:00.71,Default,,0,0,0,,In a way, my world might be wider now than it was before.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.59,0:06:08.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.59,0:06:10.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.80,0:06:12.97,Default,,0,0,0,,It's grown very cold all of a sudden, hasn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.97,0:06:14.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.10,0:06:16.93,Default,,0,0,0,,It looks like the kids have already gone to the gym.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.93,0:06:19.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I hope he's remembered to wear his jacket.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.23,0:06:20.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.40,0:06:24.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow, he's really good!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.61,0:06:26.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.15,0:06:28.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, it must have been so much work to...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.28,0:06:36.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, kid... Everyone's gone to the gym already.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.83,0:06:38.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Seriously?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.75,0:06:42.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Crap. The teacher's going to yell at me!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.04,0:06:44.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Boys can be so awful sometimes...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.09,0:06:47.42,Default,,0,0,0,,So cute! How many months old is she?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.84,0:06:50.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Almost ten months.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.43,0:06:53.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Babies are so lovely.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.81,0:06:56.52,Default,,0,0,0,,This is so nostalgic...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.89,0:07:03.06,Default,,0,0,0,,And then last week, our kid got the flu...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.85,0:07:03.56,Alt,,0,0,0,,Sorry to bother you...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.56,0:07:04.73,Alt,,0,0,0,,Not at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.06,0:07:05.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Really? That must have been hard on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.57,0:07:07.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it that season already?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.28,0:07:09.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if their fever falls, you have to keep them out of school for two days, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.95,0:07:10.86,Default,,0,0,0,,To make sure it doesn't spread.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.86,0:07:16.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm... We sent him straight back to school as soon as his fever fell.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.04,0:07:17.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Guess you have to, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.66,0:07:19.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Can't afford to lose your job.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.62,0:07:24.08,Default,,0,0,0,,And he was more or less better, so I figured the virus was dying off.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.08,0:07:25.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Guess so.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.29,0:07:29.80,Default,,0,0,0,,And even if he did pass it on, nobody would know who it came from.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.64,0:07:35.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Shall we go?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.90,0:07:49.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Um... I could actually see some sense in what they were saying,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.90,0:07:53.41,Default,,0,0,0,,and that just depressed me more.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.03,0:07:56.20,Default,,0,0,0,,What they said about work...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.20,0:07:57.62,Default,,0,0,0,,They could have been talking about me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.62,0:07:59.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.91,0:08:04.25,Default,,0,0,0,,When it gets cold, I start worrying about every little thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.25,0:08:06.50,Default,,0,0,0,,But Kouki just...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.00,0:08:09.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Put your pyjamas on, already!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.17,0:08:15.84,Default,,0,0,0,,When winter passes and it starts to get warmer,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.84,0:08:17.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I can finally relax.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.97,0:08:20.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Daikichi!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.65,0:08:29.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Daikichi, I'm just going to get my school bag. Wait here!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.57,0:08:31.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you two stupid or something?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.07,0:08:32.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Kouki, your nose!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.44,0:08:35.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I said that it was cold in the gym, and you should wear your jacket!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.49,0:08:36.91,Default,,0,0,0,,And don't run in the corridors!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.91,0:08:38.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.87,0:08:41.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I told you not to run!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.33,0:08:47.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Kouki's already starting to lose his baby teeth, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.17,0:08:50.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I keep telling him that throwing them on the roof\Ndoesn't do any good when you're in an apartment block.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.17,0:08:54.51,Note,,0,0,0,,TL Note: In some areas of Japan, kids throw their baby teeth onto the roof as a charm to make strong teeth grow in their place.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.17,0:08:54.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Lately, he won't listen to anything I say to him...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.01,0:08:58.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I'm not one to talk...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.14,0:09:00.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd strip down to my underwear...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.64,0:09:03.43,Default,,0,0,0,,...and bound down the stairs two at a time.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.81,0:09:06.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd gobble up my lunch and drink my milk in one gulp.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.19,0:09:12.03,Default,,0,0,0,,It feels really weird telling kids not to do all of the stuff that I did.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.03,0:09:15.11,Default,,0,0,0,,You did all of those things, Daikichi-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.11,0:09:17.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I think it's pretty normal for a boy,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.95,0:09:21.70,Default,,0,0,0,,which includes Kouki, I suppose...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.16,0:09:24.79,Default,,0,0,0,,S-Sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.79,0:09:30.75,Default,,0,0,0,,But if you were like that, too, then that's a load off my mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.80,0:09:40.68,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong? Walk with Kouki.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.68,0:09:41.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't want to!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.89,0:09:45.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Then how about we split into a boys' team and a girls' team?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.48,0:09:46.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't want to!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.31,0:09:50.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Rin's face is a little flushed, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.31,0:09:51.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.69,0:09:58.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I think she has a fever.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.20,0:10:02.58,Default,,0,0,0,,It might get worse...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.33,0:10:09.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Her cheeks are much more red than usual!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.88,0:10:21.39,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not the flu.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.30,0:10:25.31,Default,,0,0,0,,For now, make sure that all of her family members wear masks.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.31,0:10:27.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.06,0:10:29.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Good news, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.35,0:10:30.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.28,0:10:38.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.24,0:10:42.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you done?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.32,0:10:45.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah... I feel kind of weird around here...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.25,0:10:50.08,Default,,0,0,0,,The doctor said that it was a stomach bug, so don't force yourself...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.42,0:10:52.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah... I feel kind of...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.59,0:10:54.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Rin!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.38,0:10:57.05,Default,,0,0,0,,A washbowl!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.53,0:11:20.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Rin is...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.49,0:11:22.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Call an ambulance right away!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.45,0:11:25.53,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I've already taken her to the doctor, and we have medicine.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.53,0:11:27.41,Default,,0,0,0,,But she just won't take it!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.41,0:11:29.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Her fever's getting higher and higher, and she's in pain.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.62,0:11:32.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I suppose you didn't wrap her up warm enough?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.12,0:11:34.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Now's not the time for that!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.00,0:11:37.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Have you tried mixing the medicine in with juice?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.17,0:11:40.38,Default,,0,0,0,,You always drank it right away if it was mixed with something sweet.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.76,0:11:43.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll try it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.14,0:11:44.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks, Mum.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.19,0:11:55.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Here, have a little.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.65,0:11:56.48,Default,,0,0,0,,It's sweet.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.82,0:11:59.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Just one gulp.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.91,0:12:05.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Daikichi.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.73,0:12:35.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry to wake you so early.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.60,0:12:37.77,Default,,0,0,0,,How is Rin-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.19,0:12:39.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.23,0:12:40.86,Default,,0,0,0,,May I come in?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.03,0:12:43.24,Alt,,0,0,0,,Daikichi, what's with the hair?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.86,0:12:42.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.36,0:12:48.03,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not the flu, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.91,0:12:51.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Kouki, go watch some TV over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.33,0:12:52.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Yay!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.33,0:12:53.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Quietly, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.79,0:12:59.67,Default,,0,0,0,,She just fell asleep a little while ago, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.47,0:13:06.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Her fever keeps going up.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.97,0:13:09.05,Default,,0,0,0,,She doesn't look like she's sleeping much.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.05,0:13:11.22,Default,,0,0,0,,And she's not even sweating.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.22,0:13:13.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Has she been able to drink anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.35,0:13:17.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I was told to give her sports drinks at the very least, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.90,0:13:20.23,Default,,0,0,0,,She won't drink, and she won't eat...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.23,0:13:21.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know what to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.53,0:13:25.45,Default,,0,0,0,,W-What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.57,0:13:29.32,Default,,0,0,0,,You need to keep your cool!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.29,0:13:36.54,Default,,0,0,0,,As an adult, you have to stay calm and tell her that things are okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.08,0:13:38.63,Default,,0,0,0,,It's hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.63,0:13:41.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I've never seen her like that before.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.55,0:13:43.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't be like that. You can do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.38,0:13:46.97,Default,,0,0,0,,When children are really in trouble,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.97,0:13:49.89,Default,,0,0,0,,they need an adult by their side to help them.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.47,0:13:58.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Rin-chan will be fine as long as you're with her, Daikichi-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.36,0:14:04.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Rin-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.03,0:14:08.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Kouki-kun's mum...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.78,0:14:10.66,Default,,0,0,0,,You must be thirsty.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.66,0:14:12.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you want some ice to eat?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.47,0:14:29.55,Default,,0,0,0,,How is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.47,0:14:35.52,Default,,0,0,0,,It feels good.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.77,0:14:37.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Rin, you're awake?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.27,0:14:39.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry, I was in the bathroom.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.52,0:14:41.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Daikichi-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.48,0:14:44.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.28,0:14:48.78,Default,,0,0,0,,In a little while, try having a little more ice.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.78,0:14:52.66,Default,,0,0,0,,If you eat too much at once, you'll shock your stomach.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.66,0:14:53.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.16,0:15:01.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll put something sweet and tasty in the freezer for you, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.79,0:15:03.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.59,0:15:13.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry, you're going to be late for work, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.30,0:15:15.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Rin-chan's doing really well.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.26,0:15:19.60,Default,,0,0,0,,She'll be fine as long as you're there for her, Daikichi-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.94,0:15:22.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Right. Thank you...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.81,0:15:25.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks to you, too, Kouki.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.86,0:15:26.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Right...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.57,0:15:36.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry, I might have to take tomorrow off, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.33,0:15:38.20,Default,,0,0,0,,If anything happens, give me a call.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.20,0:15:39.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.96,0:15:41.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry for the trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.75,0:15:43.54,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.54,0:15:45.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Leave everything to us.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.96,0:15:47.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.02,0:16:01.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you eat a little?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.52,0:16:02.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.53,0:16:14.32,Default,,0,0,0,,When you're ill, you get to eat nothing but sweet things, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.29,0:16:20.54,Default,,0,0,0,,See you later...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.09,0:16:35.34,Default,,0,0,0,,After a little more rest, you'll be all better.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.14,0:16:44.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Why did it have to be Rin?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.02,0:16:47.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd shrug off a bug like this in no time at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.73,0:16:49.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.02,0:16:51.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn it! Damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.55,0:17:12.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.84,0:17:15.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Daikichi! Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.72,0:17:16.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Kouki!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.69,0:17:27.23,Default,,0,0,0,,How are you, Rin-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.23,0:17:28.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Does it hurt anywhere?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.77,0:17:31.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.44,0:17:35.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll make you some yummy rice porridge now, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.92,0:17:55.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Her fever's gone up again since this afternoon.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.05,0:17:56.17,Default,,0,0,0,,It's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.17,0:17:59.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Even without a fever, your body temperature rises as the day goes on.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.43,0:18:03.43,Default,,0,0,0,,But just a while ago, it was more than 39 degrees.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.43,0:18:06.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Here you go! Put this in the pot.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.23,0:18:07.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.69,0:18:11.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Daikichi...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.36,0:18:17.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Daikichi...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.20,0:18:23.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Water...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.25,0:18:33.00,Default,,0,0,0,,It looks really good...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.00,0:18:35.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I made some for you too, Daikichi-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.59,0:18:40.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Daikichi! Rin needs water!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.30,0:18:41.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.10,0:18:49.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Kouki, you stay in here. You don't want to catch it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.85,0:18:52.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't care if I get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.69,0:18:54.73,Default,,0,0,0,,You should care!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.70,0:19:05.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.38,0:19:16.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you, Kouki-kun...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.71,0:19:20.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Kouki, since you're around, Rin's really relaxed.{, knowing you're around, Kouki.}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.72,0:19:22.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.02,0:19:29.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Here you go, Rin-chan. Have a little.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.81,0:19:37.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry. Kouki eats this when he gets sick, as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.36,0:19:39.82,Default,,0,0,0,,It's special porridge that'll make you well in no time at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.11,0:19:42.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Kouki-kun has it, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.20,0:19:48.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Whenever he eats it, he gets better just like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.05,0:20:00.47,Default,,0,0,0,,It's good!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.89,0:20:09.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Daikichi!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.53,0:20:25.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Rin. Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.87,0:20:29.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. I feel good!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.80,0:20:48.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm hungry!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.27,0:22:25.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you tell your mum thanks for everything?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.70,0:22:30.03,Default,,0,0,0,,She looked after Rin, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.70,0:22:34.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, can I go home with you guys?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.66,0:22:36.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Again?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.04,0:22:39.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Your mum's supposed to come here to pick you up!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.83,0:22:43.80,Default,,0,0,0,,But mum's in bed with a cold.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.09,0:22:46.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?! Are you serious?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.54,0:22:54.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Let the winds of heaven
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.92,0:22:56.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Blow through the paths among the clouds
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.46,0:22:57.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}And close their gates.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.79,0:22:59.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Then for a while I could detain
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.80,0:23:01.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}These messengers in maiden form.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.63,0:23:04.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you for listening!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.97,0:23:05.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm Rin.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.10,0:23:09.81,Default,,0,0,0,,My tooth is falling out.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.81,0:23:13.39,Default,,0,0,0,,It will fall out soon, Daikichi. {It's really hard to understand this voice :p}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.98,0:23:16.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry, Daikichi.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.81,0:23:20.65,Default,,0,0,0,,The next story, also the final story, is "The First Step."
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.32,0:23:22.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Bye Bye.
